title: 'Delivered as promised'
body: Product is as described in the description, can hold suits or blazer nicely. May be folded for carrying also, however doesn't have any hanger or hooks so it is difficult to keep the same in cupboard as mine does not have hooks. Also I am not sure about the durability, only time will tell. But got two for this price, hence that is a plus

title: 'Chains are damaged every time'
body: I ordered the product twice, and had to return both times. The quality of all material is nice but the fold the metal chain in packaging which damages the chain. The product is useless if chains don't work. Alas, all they have to do is to roll and send rather than folding the product in package. Wish they would listen.
